How to set up:

3 roots:
function x = x^3 - 1
function' x = 3 * x ^ 2

reals :: [Double]
reals = [1, -1/2, -1/2]

imags :: [Double]
imags = [0, 0.86602540378, -0.86602540378]

8 roots:
function x = x^8 - 1
function' x = 8 * x ^ 7

reals :: [Double]
reals = [-1, 1, 0, 0, (-1.41/2), (-1.41/2), (1.41/2), (1.41/2)]

imags :: [Double]
imags = [0, 0, 1, -1, (1.41/2), (-1.41/2), (1.41/2), (-1.41/2)]


(IMPORTANT!) Shade cycling:
correctShade it shades = shades!!(it`mod`5)
